== [    BASIC ] ============================================================================================
   MNEMONIC: cmc [ENC: DEFAULT, MAP: DEFAULT, OPC: 0xF5]
     LENGTH:  1
        SSZ: 64
       EOSZ: 32
       EASZ: 64
   CATEGORY: FLAGOP
    ISA-SET: I86
    ISA-EXT: BASE
 EXCEPTIONS: NONE
 ATTRIBUTES: CPUFLAG_ACCESS 
  OPTIMIZED: F5 

