##       TYPE  VISIBILITY  ACTION      ENCODING   SIZE  NELEM  ELEMSZ  ELEMTYPE                        VALUE
--  ---------  ----------  ------  ------------   ----  -----  ------  --------  ---------------------------
 0   REGISTER      HIDDEN      RW          NONE     64     64       1       INT                       rflags
--  ---------  ----------  ------  ------------   ----  -----  ------  --------  ---------------------------

== [    FLAGS ] ============================================================================================
    ACTIONS: [CF  : T_M] 
       READ: 0x00000001
    WRITTEN: 0x00000001

== [      ATT ] ============================================================================================
   ABSOLUTE: cmc
   RELATIVE: cmc

== [    INTEL ] ============================================================================================
   ABSOLUTE: cmc
   RELATIVE: cmc

